188
00:20:49,680 --> 00:20:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] Sada je Trump rekao, uvešću vam carine od 5%,

189
00:20:52,920 --> 00:20:55,359
[SPEAKER_01] još bi se oni tamo ko neki pjetlići.

190
00:20:55,359 --> 00:20:58,200
