192
00:21:02,099 --> 00:21:03,319
[SPEAKER_01] da dođe na 15%.

193
00:21:03,319 --> 00:21:04,740
[SPEAKER_01] Imali su 35%.

194
00:21:04,740 --> 00:21:05,299
[SPEAKER_00] Grenland.

195
00:21:05,299 --> 00:21:09,420
[SPEAKER_00] Kako će to, ako bude, kako će to Evropa primiti?

196
00:21:09,420 --> 00:21:13,059
