210
00:22:01,039 --> 00:22:02,819
[SPEAKER_01] A ne, upravo ne.

211
00:22:02,819 --> 00:22:03,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, a?

212
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:06,000
