217
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:18,599
[SPEAKER_01] Zakon jačega.

218
00:22:18,599 --> 00:22:19,940
[SPEAKER_01] To je kraj priče.

219
00:22:19,940 --> 00:22:23,339
